      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，这是一个闭环流程。我注意到您提到了负载均衡器，这个组件在流程中会出现几次？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "负载均衡器会出现两次，分别在Redis缓存之前和之后。另外入口控制器也是首尾各有一个。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以整体是：入口控制器A → 负载均衡器B → Redis缓存C → 负载均衡器D → 入口控制器E，共五个节点，四条连线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，但注意B和D虽然是同类型的负载均衡器，但是不同的实例，A和E也是不同的入口控制器实例。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
