      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已创建五个节点：Infra_IngressController_A、Infra_LoadBalancer_B、Infra_RedisCache_C、Infra_LoadBalancer_D、Infra_IngressController_E。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "命名上我们统一用下划线风格，而且去掉后缀，直接用a、b、c、d、e作为标识，这样更简洁。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
